{"tid":2431222,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2100 眾新聞 中國組 中國5G工程漏洞？四川男買5G手機用不到5G網絡｜ 全國政協記者會：「愛國者治港」應有之義","createTime":"2021-03-03T13:08:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T21:38:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b3ec7e87f2d62ed52af2b0b479749bc355ace200","tid":2431222,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:08:49.000Z","msg":"2100 眾新聞 中國組<br />\n中國5G工程漏洞？四川男買5G手機用不到5G網絡｜<br />\n全國政協記者會：「愛國者治港」應有之義｜<br />\n大陸神醫內地假藥廣告掀爭議<br />\n (眾新聞 中國組) #眾新聞中國組​<br />\n星期一至五<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QUCoLoP7Wzg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQUCoLoP7Wzg&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX1uXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=ac2c4e5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QUCoLoP7Wzg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眾新聞<br />\n66.6K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n【眾新聞中國組｜今日有咩睇 03/03/2021】<br />\n<br />\n🔸四川的汪先生去年花4000多元購買5G手機，但最近無法使用5G網絡，電訊公司竟建議他換新手機。<br />\n<br />\n🔸政協今召開記者會，發言人郭衛民表示「愛國者治港是一國兩制的應有之義和核心要義」。<br />\n<br />\n🔸 聲稱是民族神醫「違背祖訓」的假藥廣告在網絡湧現，以致新華社發聲遏止。<br />\n<br />\n【眾新聞YouTube Channel】<a href=\"https://bit.ly/37A1PMI​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37A1PMI%E2%80%8B&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX1uXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=7079869b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/37A1PMI​</a><br />\n【眾新聞中國組全面睇】<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3ruHgdj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3ruHgdj&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX1uXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=5ffa3a41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3ruHgdj</a>"},{"pid":"268301f2b50bd386e39734f732ff11221ae70796","tid":2431222,"uid":129883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:10:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5135b92cd8829775b6fe0cd384a5aa1f10508111","tid":2431222,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T14:30:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgm